prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Retro High Pine Green Black
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/High/Jordan 1 Retro High Pine Green Black
prod.desciption:
ordan Brand added new colors to a classic silhouette with the Jordan 1 Retro High Pine Green Black, now available on StockX. This colorway draws inspiration from the Jordan 1 Retro High Pine Green from 2019, only this time the entire upper features black and pine green hues.

This Jordan 1 High is comprised of a black tumbled leather upper with green leather overlays. A Gym Red embroidered tongue tag, sail midsole, and pine green outsole completes this design. These sneakers released in February of 2020 and retailed for $170.

If you are looking for the Jordan 1 Retro High Pine Green 2018 click HERE.
